---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Applications
description: Stabplast additives and stabilizer systems for PVC pipes, fittings, profiles, foam boards, wires & cables, sheets, WPC, roofing, footwear and paints.
permalink: /applications/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container page-hero__inner">
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</li>
        <li aria-current="page">Applications</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>
    <span class="page-hero__eyebrow">Applications we serve</span>
    <h1>Applications</h1>
    <p>Stabplast Chemo Industries manufactures PVC additives and stabilizer systems for a wide range of PVC applications — from pipes and profiles to foam boards, cables, footwear and paints.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid--3">
      {% for app in applications %}
      {% if app.detail %}
      <a class="card" id="{{ app.slug }}" href="/applications/{{ app.slug }}/">
        <div class="card__media">
          {% image app.image, app.alt, "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 360px" %}
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <h2 class="card__title">{{ app.name }}</h2>
          <p>{{ app.summary }}</p>
          <span class="card__link">Explore application →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      {% else %}
      <article class="card" id="{{ app.slug }}">
        <div class="card__media">
          {% image app.image, app.alt, "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 360px" %}
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <h2 class="card__title">{{ app.name }}</h2>
          <p>{{ app.summary }}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ KEY ADVANTAGES ============ -->
<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Why Stabplast</span>
      <h2>Key advantages of Stabplast products</h2>
    </div>
    <ul class="prop-list prop-list--cols">
      <li>High whiteness and colour consistency</li>
      <li>Excellent weather resistance</li>
      <li>Wide processing window</li>
      <li>Superior surface finish</li>
      <li>Excellent impact strength</li>
      <li>Low cycle time</li>
      <li>Customized formulations</li>
      <li>Lead and Calcium-Zinc systems available</li>
      <li>Suitable for high-speed extrusion and moulding</li>
      <li>Technical support for customer-specific applications</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container cta-band__inner">
    <div>
      <h2>Have a specific application in mind?</h2>
      <p>We'll match the right stabilizer or stearate to your process and end-use.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-band__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.quote.href }}">{{ site.cta.quote.label }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
